your Li family holds immense power in Jialong.

43
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,000
But this is Bian Shui.

44
00:03:10,599 --> 00:03:12,360
I still have my brothers from Ghost Face Hall.

45
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,680
If we really fight to mutual destruction,

46
00:03:15,439 --> 00:03:16,560
that wouldn't be appropriate, would it?

47
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:18,479
Second Master Tang is right!

48
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,280
Young Master Li,

49
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:21,840
this mine contains gold worth billions.

50
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,520
If our two families cooperate,

51
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:24,800
with your Li family taking the lion's share,

52
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,000
your Li family

53
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:27,240
will firmly suppress

54
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:27,919
Jialong,

55
00:03:27,919 --> 00:03:28,719
Lika,

56
00:03:28,719 --> 00:03:30,520
and all the families in Badi.

57
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,520
Securing the top spot in the southwest!

58
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,159
You could become the richest!

59
00:03:35,159 --> 00:03:36,960
Young Master Li is amazing!

60
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,080
Young Master Li,

61
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,919
I know Zhao Fengsheng

62
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:42,000
worked with you in Amir.

63
00:03:42,479 --> 00:03:44,319
Will you really give up such huge profits

64
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,000
for this nobody?

65
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,360
A nobody?

66
00:03:49,879 --> 00:03:51,439
If my boss is a nobody,

67
00:03:51,879 --> 00:03:53,039
